            <description sparkle:format="markdown"><![CDATA[# Fastband Core 0.1.6

## Highlights

- Adds portable product manifests so registered products can move cleanly between compatible Fastband Core workspaces.
- Expands environment workflows for creating, viewing, and managing local development environments.
- Surfaces current AIM presence in Fastband Core, keeping active coordination information available to operators.
- Corrects Fastband Core artwork across the application’s branded surfaces.
]]></description>
